+ 
+ STARTTEST
+ :set hidden nocp nu rnu
+ :redir @a | set nu? rnu? | redir END
+ :e! xx
+ :redir @b | set nu? rnu? | redir END
+ :e! #
+ :$put ='results:'
+ :$put a
+ :$put b
+ :/^results/,$w! test.out
+ :q!
+ ENDTEST
